{"tid":660914,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"藍芽技術聯盟停止ZTE會員資格&產品認證","createTime":"2018-05-11T05:56:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-20T02:51:48.000Z","uid":10717,"like":76,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"1eb6f24cc97aa0e9b1c83da5404ccd6a2ca7c0ee","tid":660914,"uid":10717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T05:56:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/11/135603_aa9e057c7d2db9861752a5a0afd20d7c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F11%2F135603_aa9e057c7d2db9861752a5a0afd20d7c.png&h=3bed2f96&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大家都在吵晶片商如何、找哪一家公司可以填補美國不供貨的同時<br />\n<br />\n殺手鐧:直接把你技術認證停掉<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n藍芽技術聯盟直接停了ZTE的會員資格+所有ZTE相關員工的帳戶<br />\n<br />\n因此在恢復ZTE會員資格之前(等同於美國商務部禁令解除之前)<br />\n<br />\nZTE將無法得到藍芽技術的認證與更新 也沒辦法參與藍芽技術的發展<br />\n<br />\n因此 即使MTK給了手機晶片 ZTE也沒辦法出藍芽認證...<br />\n<br />\n----<br />\n這第一槍 接下來還有 wifi? LTE?"},{"pid":"5450ed087a27d260a0fb8d1b92b502335ab4ba71","tid":660914,"uid":20208,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T06:09:41.000Z","msg":"而加真係有齊硬件都無撚用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c7883459ceef45eca0edfee4d9ccf36b9626e4d","tid":660914,"uid":121686,"like":49,"dislike":0,"score":49,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T06:11:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/11/141116_43e26f1acd1d302adb9c28655a444118.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F11%2F141116_43e26f1acd1d302adb9c28655a444118.png&h=a58abf1b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3e8a5e0f1b79d22a4cfacc5a48aa32bcde76d69b","tid":660914,"uid":17550,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T06:14:20.000Z","msg":"又贏"},{"pid":"c312c2c593df160f6a652ae138dd9472f8d2b699","tid":660914,"uid":39365,"like":38,"dislike":1,"score":37,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T06:17:13.000Z",